-- Endemol Considers Merger With John de Mol’s Talpa, Dagblad Says
-- B y   M a a i k e   N o o r d h u i s
-- 2012-05-29T05:45:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-29/endemol-considers-merger-with-john-de-mol-s-talpa-dagblad-says.html
Endemol NV is considering merging
with John de Mol’s Talpa Media Holding NV, Het Financieele
Dagblad cited Endemol Chief Financial Officer Just Spee as
saying in an interview.  The producer of the “Big Brother” TV shows needs to
complete its debt restructuring before it can make a large
strategic move, the newspaper said, citing Spee.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maaike Noordhuis in Amsterdam at 
 mnoordhuis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  